# CONFLUENCE_PAT — Confluence Server/DC Personal Access Token (Bearer auth).
#   Create one at: <your-confluence>/plugins/personalaccesstokens/usertokens.action
#   (or: profile picture → Settings → Personal Access Tokens → Create token).
#   Set a name + expiry. The token is shown only once on creation — copy it before closing the dialog.
#
# CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL — Root URL of your install. No trailing slash, no /rest/api.
#   Canonical value lives at: Confluence admin → General Configuration → Server Base URL.
#   Shapes: https://confluence.example.com    or    https://example.com/confluence    (with context path).
CONFLUENCE_PAT=
CONFLUENCE_BASE_URL=
